data.description: Welcome to this exceptional residence, expertly curated for a discerning homeowner. Nestled on a sprawling 14.8-acre canvas, this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom haven is more than just move-in readyit's an invitation to a lifestyle of comfort and sophistication.As you enter, you'll be greeted by an expansive open floor plan. The kitchen, a culinary masterpiece, showcases granite countertops, a gas stove, stainless steel appliances, custom cabinet doors, and an enchanting farmhouse industrial ambiance.The owner's suite is a sanctuary of luxury, featuring a generous walk-in closet and a private ensuite adorned with a soaking tub and shower. Meanwhile, the guest bedrooms offer ample space, enhanced by built-in storage and new carpets installed just this year.Beyond the main dwelling, discover a 30x40 shop boasting 100 amp service, a separate meter, and endless possibilities. A seasonal pond and spring add natural charm, while 2 RV pads with sewer and water hookups, an additional 10x10 pad, 2 wells, a tankless water heater, and a partially finished basement amplify the property's allure.This residence is not just a home; it's an embodiment of thoughtful design and practical amenities. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yoursschedule your exclusive tour today and envision the lifestyle that awaits you.
